###  http://www.semanticweb.org/lenovo/ontologies/2026/3/FloodControlDispatchOntology#Aqueduct
:Aqueduct rdf:type owl:Class ;
          rdfs:subClassOf :WaterConservancyProject ;
          rdfs:comment "渡槽" .


